00:25:55,530 --> 00:25:57,330
Sa lahat ng nangyari kani-kanina lang,

501
00:25:58,660 --> 00:26:00,700
Sobrang nag-aalala ako sa batang ito.

502
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:03,460
Kaya iniisip kong feeling out siya

503
00:26:03,460 --> 00:26:05,460
mamaya habang kumakain kami.

504
00:26:05,460 --> 00:26:06,720
Sa tingin mo ba ito ay angkop?

505
00:26:16,570 --> 00:26:17,410
Lolo,

506
00:26:18,490 --> 00:26:19,330
iyong hearing aid.

507
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:22,540
Nanay?

508
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:24,980
Hindi nag-set up si Dad
ang VCD player para sa iyo?

509
00:26:25,570 --> 00:26:28,250
Maaari ba akong umasa sa kanya para sa anumang bagay?

510
00:26:28,250 --> 00:26:30,270
Ibinalik niya ito
at iniwan lang ito sa may pintuan.

511
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:33,180
Ang amplifier at ang VCD player
ay dinala pabalik sa dalawang magkahiwalay na biyahe.

512
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:35,180
Pinalamanan ko lang sila
sa ilalim ng higaan ng lolo mo.

513
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:37,330
Dahil nakauwi ka ngayon,
maaari mo ba akong tulungan sa pag-set up nito?

514
00:26:38,050 --> 00:26:38,890
Oo naman.

515
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:40,460
Nasaan ang VCD player?

516
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:41,420
Wala sa ilalim ng kama.

517
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:43,460
Baka nasa storage room?

518
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,300
Tingnan mo ito.

519
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:14,570
Ilang tao na ang nagsabi sa akin dati

520
00:27:14,570 --> 00:27:15,620
na lasa ng bagay na ito

521
00:27:15,620 --> 00:27:17,490
medyo parang plastik.

522
00:27:17,490 --> 00:27:19,180
Walang magiging problema, tama ba?

523
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,480
Ang sarap lang ng tubig.

524
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:22,770
Nasaan ang packaging box?

525
00:27:22,770 --> 00:27:24,220
Tapusin natin ito.

526
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:25,420
Segunda-mano ito, Tatay.

527
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:27,250
Matagal nang nawala ang packaging.

528
00:27:30,220 --> 00:27:31,730
Direktor Tong, narinig mo

529
00:27:31,730 --> 00:27:32,900
malinaw naman ang sinabi ko diba?

530
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:48,620
Nasaan si Hui? Saan siya nagpunta?

531
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:49,660
hindi ko alam.

532
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:51,310
Sinabi niya lang na tutulungan niya ako
kasama ang VCD player,

533
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:52,530
tapos tumakbo siya palabas ng walang sabi-sabi.

534
00:27:54,420 --> 00:27:56,630
Hindi ka man lang nagpalit ng sapatos.
saan ka pupunta

535
00:27:57,010 --> 00:27:58,660
Hongbing, handa na ang pagkain.

536
00:27:58,660 --> 00:27:59,620
Halika at kumain.

537
00:28:11,460 --> 00:28:12,330
saan ka pupunta

538
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,820
Babalik ako saglit.

539
00:28:34,860 --> 00:28:35,810
Hayaan akong tumawag.

540
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,290
Malaking lalaki,

541
00:28:42,290 --> 00:28:43,530
si Chen Hongbing ito.

542
00:28:43,530 --> 00:28:44,700
Namatay yung phone ko.

543
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:46,460
Makinig ng mabuti. Magdala ng ilang tao

544
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:47,980
papunta sa washing pool
sa coal washing plant.

545
00:28:47,980 --> 00:28:48,820
Oo, sa ngayon.

546
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:56,980
(Golden Peony)

547
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:12,700
(Heyi Coal Washing Plant, Fengyang Town)

548
00:29:29,660 --> 00:29:30,940
Tatay,

549
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,250
wag na tayong maghintay.

550
00:29:32,250 --> 00:29:33,180
Ikukuha kita ng sopas.

551
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:54,460
Ding Yue,

552
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,260
Ako...

553
00:29:58,420 --> 00:30:00,110
Gusto kitang hilingin
happy birthday muna.

554
00:30:01,570 --> 00:30:02,620
Salamat, Tatay.

555
00:30:02,620 --> 00:30:03,940
Sa loob ng mahigit 20 taon,

556
00:30:05,250 --> 00:30:06,090
ang pamilyang ito

557
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:08,420
parang tahanan lang

558
00:30:09,980 --> 00:30:11,460
dahil sayo.

559
00:30:12,730 --> 00:30:14,050
Sa mga susunod na araw,

560
00:30:15,090 --> 00:30:16,290
Aasa pa rin ako sayo.

561
00:30:17,050 --> 00:30:18,570
Huwag hayaan ang pamilyang ito

562
00:30:18,570 --> 00:30:19,660
magkawatak-watak.

563
00:30:23,090 --> 00:30:23,930
Tatay,

564
00:30:25,330 --> 00:30:26,250
wag ka mag alala.

565
00:30:31,940 --> 00:30:33,010
Tara kain na tayo.

566
00:30:34,250 --> 00:30:35,460
Bilisan mo at inumin mo ang iyong sopas.

567
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,620
Kung hindi, lalamig ito.

568
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:37,940
Okay.

569
00:30:37,940 --> 00:30:38,780
Mabuti.

